 "remarks": "Direct waterfront location in the desirable East Norwalk beach community. Enjoy panoramic water views, captivating sunsets, and gentle summer breezes from your expansive balcony, accessed from the living room/dining room and primary bedroom sliders (new 2021) overlooking L.I. Sound &amp; Harbor. Features a new kitchen and recently updated primary en suite bath. Luxurious amenities include a community room for social gatherings, an in-ground heated waterfront pool, a waterfront promenade, and a marina. Walk or bike to all East Norwalk amenities: beaches, train stations, shops, restaurants, dog park, SoNo Collection Mall, restaurants, and the Maritime Aquarium. Minutes to I-95 and Merritt Parkway. Commuters&apos; delight, only 50 miles north of NYC. Secured building with elevators, a storage room, and reserved carport parking spot S19. Come live and enjoy all that waterfront living and the beach area of East Norwalk has to offer. It&apos;s a wonderful lifestyle! A boat slip may be available for rent.  **Note:** Reserves build-up assessment $377.50 to June 2030, and flood insurance is included in monthly HOA.",
